                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-106-off520 t18170917-106-cd521"></join>, sixty yards of carpet, value 15l.; one ring, value 20s.; and one canvas wrapper, value 1s. 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
